sequenceDiagram
  actor Student
  participant Web as React Web Client
  participant API as TutorController
  participant Auth as AuthGuard
  participant Tutor as TutorService
  participant Curriculum as CurriculumService
  participant Lesson as LessonService
  participant Verifier as MathVerifierService
  participant MasteryPolicy as MasteryPolicyService
  participant Decision as LessonDecisionService
  participant LessonPolicy as LessonPolicyService
  participant Profile as StudentProfileService
  participant Background as BackgroundAiService
  participant Knowledge as KnowledgeService
  participant DB as SQLite
  participant AIModel as AiModelService
  participant Policy as AiOperationPolicyService
  participant Usage as UsageService
  participant OpenAI as OpenAI-backed model provider

  Student->>Web: Open tutor workspace
  Web->>API: GET /tutor/lessons?scope=active
  API->>Auth: Validate session cookie
  Auth-->>API: Authenticated user
  API->>Tutor: getLessonHistory(scope active)
  Tutor->>DB: Read non-terminal lesson_sessions and recent tutor_turns
  Tutor-->>API: Active lesson records
  API-->>Web: Resumable active lessons
  Web->>API: GET /tutor/lessons?scope=history
  API->>Tutor: getLessonHistory(scope history)
  Tutor->>DB: Read terminal lesson_sessions and legacy tutor_turn records
  Tutor-->>API: Read-only historical records
  API-->>Web: Finished and legacy records
  opt Student finishes active lesson
    Student->>Web: Click finish lesson
    Web->>API: POST /tutor/lessons/:lessonSessionId/finish
    API->>Auth: Validate session cookie
    Auth-->>API: Authenticated user
    API->>Tutor: finishLesson(user, lessonSessionId)
    Tutor->>Lesson: finishSessionWithTransition(userId, lessonSessionId)
    Lesson->>DB: Mark own active lesson_sessions row finished only if non-terminal
    Lesson-->>Tutor: Finished lesson session and transitioned flag
    opt First actual terminal transition
      Tutor->>Background: enqueueLessonClosureReview(lesson_finished)
    end
    Tutor-->>API: Archived history item
    API-->>Web: Open read-only record
  end

  Student->>Web: Type prompt or use speech recognition
  Web->>API: POST /tutor/message with lessonType and requestId
  API->>Auth: Validate session cookie
  Auth-->>API: Authenticated user
  API->>Tutor: answerMessage(user, message, source, lessonType, requestId)
  Tutor->>DB: Check tutor_turns by requestId
  alt Duplicate requestId
    DB-->>Tutor: Stored TutorAnswer
    Tutor-->>API: Cached answer and usage snapshot
    API-->>Web: Cached response
  else New request
  Tutor->>Curriculum: resolve(message)
  Curriculum->>DB: Read active curriculum_skills
  Curriculum-->>Tutor: topicId, skillId, taskTypeId, verifierKind
  Tutor->>Lesson: beginTurnWithTransitions(userId, conversationId, lessonType, topicId)
  Lesson->>DB: Touch non-terminal lesson, reject terminal reuse, and close only confirmed boundaries
  DB-->>Lesson: Scoped progress/regression rows
  Lesson-->>Tutor: Lesson lifecycle, strategy signal, and actual closedSessions
  opt Actual closedSessions returned
    Tutor->>Background: enqueueLessonClosureReview(superseded or type drift)
  end
  alt Hard learning limit reached
    Tutor->>DB: Insert local stop tutor_turn
    Tutor->>Background: enqueueLessonClosureReview(hard limit)
    Tutor-->>API: TutorAnswer with stop lifecycle
    API-->>Web: Stop response and usage snapshot
  else Tutor may continue
  Tutor->>Verifier: verifyPendingTaskAttempt(message, lessonSessionId)
  Verifier->>DB: Read pending lesson_tasks and insert student_attempts
  Verifier->>DB: Read source_task_id, hint ladder, and common_errors
  Verifier->>MasteryPolicy: evaluateVerifiedAttempt(skillId, verifier result)
  MasteryPolicy->>DB: Read active curriculum_mastery_criteria and cross-lesson source_task successes
  MasteryPolicy-->>Verifier: Mastery policy accepted or needs more evidence
  opt Incorrect answer with common_errors
    Verifier->>DB: Read curriculum_misconceptions for adaptive hint
  end
  opt Mastery policy accepted
    Verifier->>DB: Insert mastery_evidence and verified progress row
  end
  DB-->>Verifier: Verifier evidence
  Verifier-->>Tutor: Backend verifier evidence
  Tutor->>Profile: getTutorContext(userId)
  Profile->>DB: Read student_profiles
  DB-->>Profile: Profile summary and strategy
  Profile-->>Tutor: Tutor profile context
  Tutor->>Decision: decide(message, lifecycle, profile, curriculum, verifier evidence, allowed tools)
  Decision->>AIModel: lessonDecision operation
  AIModel->>Policy: Resolve lessonDecision policy
  Policy-->>AIModel: Decision role, model, optional service tier
  AIModel->>OpenAI: Responses API request
  OpenAI-->>AIModel: LessonDecision JSON
  AIModel->>Usage: Record decision usage
  Usage->>DB: Insert ai_usage_ledger
  AIModel-->>Decision: Decision response
  Decision->>LessonPolicy: Validate proposed actions
  LessonPolicy-->>Decision: Accepted/rejected action results
  Decision->>DB: Insert lesson_decisions and route profile deltas to background observations
  Decision-->>Tutor: Decision and backend policy result
  Tutor->>Knowledge: getActiveVectorStoreIds()
  Knowledge->>DB: Read env ids, project_ai_resources, or active knowledge_files
  Knowledge-->>Tutor: Vector store ids
  Tutor->>AIModel: Create tutor operation response with lifecycle, curriculum, verifier evidence, decision policy, profile context, lesson type, usage context, and optional file_search
  AIModel->>Policy: Resolve tutorAnswer or tutorAnswerWithRag policy
  Policy-->>AIModel: Role, model, metadata, optional service tier
  AIModel->>OpenAI: Responses API request
  OpenAI-->>AIModel: Structured tutor JSON blocks and citations
  AIModel->>Usage: Record operation usage when usage context exists
  Usage->>DB: Insert ai_usage_ledger
  AIModel-->>Tutor: Provider response
  Tutor->>Verifier: ensureBackendTask(answer, curriculum)
  Verifier->>DB: Select active task_bank_tasks for supported vertical
  alt Imported task-bank task found
    Verifier->>DB: Insert lesson_tasks from imported task with source_task_id, hint ladder, and common_errors
  else Empty-DB POC fallback
    Verifier->>DB: Insert logged generated fallback unless TASK_BANK_REQUIRED=true
  end
  Verifier-->>Tutor: Pending backend task evidence
  Tutor->>Lesson: completeTurn(model goal suggestion, decision policy, answer shape)
  Lesson->>DB: Accept goal only through backend policy, update lesson_sessions and insert lesson_effectiveness_signals
  Tutor->>DB: Insert tutor_turn with requestId and lesson_type
  Tutor->>Background: enqueueTutorTurnWork()
  opt Lesson became terminal through first confirmed transition
    Tutor->>Background: enqueueLessonClosureReview(goal reached)
  end
  alt Background batching enabled
    Background->>DB: Insert background_learning_observations with lesson_type
    Background->>DB: Schedule or reschedule learning_window_analysis job
  else Legacy background mode
    Background->>DB: Insert per-turn background_ai_jobs
  end
  Tutor->>Usage: Read lesson/day usage snapshot
  Usage->>DB: Summarize ai_usage_ledger
  Tutor-->>API: TutorAnswer with lesson lifecycle, usage, debug, and ordered blocks
  API-->>Web: Lesson type, lifecycle, usage/debug, text, task, example, image blocks, citations
  Web->>API: GET /usage/me/summary
  API->>Usage: getUserSummary(userId, lessonSessionId)
  Usage->>DB: Read ai_usage_ledger, lesson_decisions, mastery_evidence, and background_ai_jobs for signed-in user
  API-->>Web: Usage/debug summary with safe background job previews
  end
  end
  Note over Background,AIModel: Later drain groups stored observations by window size, idle timeout, quality trigger, or lesson closure
  Background->>DB: Recover stale queued observations and running jobs
  Background->>DB: Read pending observations and job queue
  Background->>DB: Mark selected observations queued
  Background->>AIModel: Learning-window operation with optional prompt cache key
  AIModel->>Policy: Resolve backgroundLearningWindow policy
  Policy-->>AIModel: Background role, model, optional service tier
  AIModel->>OpenAI: Responses API request
  OpenAI-->>AIModel: Learning-window JSON
  AIModel->>Usage: Record background operation usage
  Usage->>DB: Insert ai_usage_ledger
  AIModel-->>Background: Parsed model response
  Background->>DB: Store analysis window, signals, session summaries, skill progress, processed observations
  alt Window analysis fails
    Background->>DB: Return claimed observations to pending
  end
  opt Profile refresh interval reached
    Background->>AIModel: Combined profile/strategy refresh operation
    AIModel->>Policy: Resolve backgroundProfileStrategyRefresh policy
    Policy-->>AIModel: Background role, model, optional service tier
    AIModel->>OpenAI: Responses API request
    OpenAI-->>AIModel: Profile and strategy patch JSON
    AIModel-->>Background: Parsed model response
    Background->>DB: Update student_profiles
  end
  opt Image block present
    Student->>Web: Request diagram from image block
    Web->>API: POST /tutor/image
    API->>Tutor: generateImage(prompt, context, lessonSessionId)
    Tutor->>AIModel: Generate tutorImage operation PNG
    AIModel->>Policy: Resolve tutorImage policy
    Policy-->>AIModel: Image role and model
    AIModel->>OpenAI: Images API request
    OpenAI-->>AIModel: Base64 image
    AIModel->>Usage: Record image usage
    Usage->>DB: Insert ai_usage_ledger
    AIModel-->>Tutor: Image response
    Tutor-->>API: Data URL and usage snapshot
    API-->>Web: Render generated image and refresh usage
  end
